dmca.title: TV DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google: Android Market

works.description:
I have spent 5 years collecting this  
information, and even though I give it away for free on the website, I
have  
not allowed redistribution of the material through other websites or apps.

The app in question is automatically fetching this list. The functionality
 
of the app is to automatically block incoming calls from telemarketers,  
which is the exact same functionality of my own app, Hysj!  
(https://market.android.com/details?id=no.edev.hysj.android.v1&feature=search_result#?t=W251bGwsMSwxLDEsIm5vLmVkZXYuaHlzai5hbmRyb2lkLnYxIl0).

As I said, I give away the information on the website for free, but I was 

hoping to make a little money from the sale of apps.
